    <div class="col-2 col-lg-8">
      <h1>Cheesecake</h1>
      <p>
          <a>
          <img src="https://images.freshop.com/6936610/87351433e8735bda59deceaaefa6b4ae_medium.png" />
          <img src="https://images.freshop.com/00022710100000/87779fd1e78695b627a6f0d0f5bbc1b0_medium.png" />

          </a>
        </p>

    </div>


    <div class="col-3 col-lg-3">
  <h4>Prep/Cook Time</h4>
  <table class="table table-bordered">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>35 minutes</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<div class="col-6 col-lg-3">
  <h4>Ingredients</h4>
  <table class="table table-bordered">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>1/4 c. butter <% if (profile_set) { %> <span class="label label-danger"> Missing </span> <% } %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>1 c. graham cracker crumbs <% if (profile_set) { %> <span class="label label-warning"> Untracked </span> <% } %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>3 tbsp. packed brown sugar</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>1/3 c. chopped pecans <% if (profile_set) { %> <span class="label label-danger"> Missing </span> <% } %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>2 (8 oz) packages cream cheese, softened</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>



<div class="col-6 col-lg-8">
  <h2>Recipe</h2>
  <table class="table table-bordered">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>1. To Make Crust: Melt butter or margarine in a small saucepan. Stir in graham cracker crumbs, 3 tablespoons brown sugar, and 1/3 cup chopped nuts. Pack into ungreased 9 or 9 1/2 inch springform pan.</td>

      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>2. To Make Filling: Beat cream cheese and 1 1/4 cups brown sugar together until smooth and fluffy. Slowly beat in eggs one at a time, just until blended. Stir in 1 teaspoon rum flavoring, 1 teaspoon vanilla, 1/4 cup sour cream, and 1/3 cup chopped nuts. Pour filling into pan.</td>

      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>3. Bake at 350 degrees F (175 degrees C) for about 25 to 30 minutes, until set. Remove pan to cake rack while you prepare topping.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>4. To Make Topping: Stir together 1 1/2 cups sour cream, 1/4 cup brown sugar, maple flavoring, and 1/2 teaspoon rum flavoring. Spread over cheesecake. Return to oven, and bake for 10 minutes. Loosen sides of cake. Cool until almost room temperature, then chill for a few hours before serving.</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>



<div class="col-6 col-lg-3">
  <h4>Tools & Utensils</h4>
